description: Try our easy to follow Carrot Chips recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Savoury pie & tart,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Sesame free,Halal,Soy free,Vegetarian,Vegan,Low fat,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Carrot Chips Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place semolina, salt and paprika into cup and combine.
Place carrot sticks on a baking paper lined tray. Spray with olive oil and sprinkle over the semolina mixture. Grill for 5 to 10 minutes, or until the tops begin to colour.
Serve as a snack, or as an accompaniment to your lunch or dinner. Dip your carrot chips in a simple garlic aioli or avocado dip.
